{"Author":null,"Body":"<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 18.649999618530273px 12px 0px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(35, 40, 35); font-family: arial, serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Aalto Global Impact hosted the second training workshop from the series “Training Program on Innovation Policy for ICT” during 10-14 September 2012 in Helsinki, Finland. 15 senior policy-makers and representatives of key governmental organizations from Burkina Faso, Ghana, India, Kenya, Philippines, Uganda, South Africa, and Tanzania, as well as <\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">5 senior officials from the World Bank headquarters and one from country office in Senegal <\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">participated in this <\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">5-days-long intensive training course<\/span><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">. The progam included a <\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">day trip to the city of Tampere.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 18.649999618530273px 12px 0px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(35, 40, 35); font-family: arial, serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">During the first workshop (4-9 June 2012) participants came from Morocco, Tunisia, Egypt, Lebanon, Moldova, Armenia, Georgia &nbsp;and Mexico, as well as four senior officials from the World Bank headquarters in Washington DC.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 18.649999618530273px 12px 0px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(35, 40, 35); font-family: arial, serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">The trainings were part of the piloting initiative by The World Bank ICT Sector Unit, together with infoDev, the Ministry for Foreign Affairs of Finland and Aalto University. The objective of these training workshops is to develop the learning of participating decision makers on strategic innovation policy in the field of ICT, in a multidisciplinary and multicultural setting. The approach is to engage the decision-makers in a hands-on, participatory and real-life case study analysis that involve also prototyping and testing of concepts, business models and service designs. <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 18.649999618530273px 12px 0px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(35, 40, 35); font-family: arial, serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Professor Mikko Koria designed and facilitated both trainings, with support from Aalto Global Impact team; and over 20 speakers from different Finnish organizations shared their insights with the participants during each training.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 18.649999618530273px 12px 0px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(35, 40, 35); font-family: arial, serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">“As representatives of the public sector in various developing countries, we had the marvelous chance to be immersed in innovation for six consecutive days. This learning experience has touched us and we hope to put it in action so that it, in turn, touches the people of our countries to many years to come.”, commented one of the participants - Mr Firas Abi-Nassif, Advisor to the Minister at Lebanese Ministry of Telecommunications. <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 18.649999618530273px 12px 0px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(35, 40, 35); font-family: arial, serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cambria; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Mrs. Sally Metwally, Innovation Support Director at Technology, Innovation &amp; Entrepreneurship Center (TIEC) in Egypt gave us feedback that she is very grateful to the organizers and the participants “for creating such a wonderful learning environment”.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>","CategoryCollection":{"CollectionContent":[],"ID":"07b35796-1309-4c28-9999-2d666d40720e","MasterETag":null,"Name":"CategoryCollection","OwnerID":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","RelativeLocation":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP\/CategoryCollection\/07b35796-1309-4c28-9999-2d666d40720e","SemanticDomainName":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP"},"Excerpt":"“Training Program on Innovation Policy for ICT” during 10-14 September 2012 in Helsinki, Finland","FeaturedImage":{"Caption":null,"ID":"f9ddf33c-9b20-48aa-860a-d1e74febb622","ImageData":{"ContentLength":0,"FileExt":null,"ID":"19f7e3ba-eeb5-4e9e-8d4b-7402f5f7b100","MasterETag":null,"Name":"MediaContent","OriginalFileName":null,"OwnerID":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","RelativeLocation":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP\/MediaContent\/19f7e3ba-eeb5-4e9e-8d4b-7402f5f7b100","SemanticDomainName":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP"},"MasterETag":null,"Name":"Image","OwnerID":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","RelativeLocation":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP\/Image\/f9ddf33c-9b20-48aa-860a-d1e74febb622","SemanticDomainName":"AaltoGlobalImpact.OIP","Title":null},"ID":"045e9d00-74b7-4ccb-b503-936362862cc5","ImageGroup":{"Description":null,"ID":"3561502b-3c14-41ab-a192-705cf074a709","